      "date": "2012-11-06 23:26:27.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on el6/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/57836c16-2869-11e2-9c12-52540035b04c).  Ran 2 tests.  1 tests failed: lustre-initialization-1.",
